an Vaerenbergh - Focus/ Le Vif)\r\n-  \"Un ton inimitable et plein de charme\"  (Eric Adam - DBD)", "status": "ok", "pages": 48, "black_and_white": false, "book": "album cartonné", "writers": ["Bocquet José-Louis", "Rivière"], "date": "2016-08-26"}
